{
  "stem": "26142.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It-- it was-- and while we are at the subject of return to Zion, I have to tell you that my great-grandfather, after whom I am named, that means my mother's grandfather-- his name was Michael Drimmer.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was the first Jew that emigrated to Palestine in 1903.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was-- he was in his early 60s.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was such a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He-- he-- and this is more or less-- he-- he felt a messianic mission that he was able to-- he left his entire family, his children, whatever he owned.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He left with his wife and went to Jerusalem.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And at that time, the Ottoman Empire-- the-- the-- the Turkey-- had-- Palestine was under the Ottoman Empire control.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the-- the-- the belief in the return-- that the Jewish people will return to-- to Zion was so strong in him.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was such a-- such a-- in our-- in our area, they talked a lot about him, because he was-- he came-- he was born in Dolyna, and on the other side-- well, that was Austria-Hungary.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was one country before World War I.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he used to be the-- the-- the cantor for the high holidays.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Of course, he-- he did that as-- as-- that wasn't a paid-- paid-- paid position.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was an honor to-- to be-- to be the-- the cantor.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he brought over the melodies that were-- that were used in-- in Galicia and-- and that area, when he came over to live in the-- in the Carpathians.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in 1903, he got up, and he left.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My uncle, [INAUDIBLE], where I was with him in 1941, he told me the story that he helped him.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He helped get the papers.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
